        },
        {
            "title": "【異動板塊】金礦股造好 金價創新高突破3200美元關",
            "description": "<p>金價創新高，突破3200美元關，金礦股造好。</p>\n<p>招金(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01818' >01818</a>)急升7.1%；山東黃金(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01787' >01787</a>)飆8%；靈寶黃金(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/03330' >03330</a>)急揚7.6%；中國黃金國際(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02099' >02099</a>)彈升8.8%；赤峰黃金(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/06693' >06693</a>)漲3.4%；SPDR金(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02840' >02840</a>)急漲3.1%；紫金(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02899' >02899</a>)彈升4.7%。</p>\n<p>金價今早再創新高，突破3200美元關，一度升至3219.48美元，升1.4%，新造3214.76美元，仍漲1.2%。</p>\n<p>立即試用<a href=\"https://www.ejfq.com/home.htm?source=sapo9\" target=\"_blank\">EJFQ「信號」全方位股票分析系統</a>，運用100+選股條件篩選值博股！</p>   </div>\n        ",
